    <intervention_name>Viusid</intervention_name>
    <description>One Viusid bag (4 grams, orally administered) every 8 hours, for 6 days in combination with the conventional treatment consisting in: intramuscular injection of one bulb of Dipyrone (600 mg) every 8 hours if fever is greater or equal to 38 ºC; intramuscular injection of one bulb of dimenhydrinate (50 mg) every 8 hours if vomiting; oral rehydration solution (8 ounce) after each diarrhea.</description>
